{"tid":268102,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"又一間令人失望既沾麵","createTime":"2017-06-02T18:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T16:57:43.000Z","uid":62277,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"991aadeba8d9a23cd8a04963e1956c56efd1c114","tid":268102,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:12:54.000Z","msg":"揀左冷麵,一樣都係腍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n辛辣沾麵<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/boz32tm5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fboz32tm5&h=bb652fe4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2362dbf45767f1512d6d064fa414772e8a0d9590","tid":268102,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:14:19.000Z","msg":"蛋花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c13a04f568a4d5740906b00efd29687c832ac1","tid":268102,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T23:24:40.000Z","msg":"食過湯麵，D麵硬過鐵線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔熟嘅<br />\n<br />\n沾麵唔係好食D咩？"},{"pid":"c9804aa5a575f7a282ec98089ff33406f87f4dc1","tid":268102,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T23:30:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食過湯麵，D麵硬過鐵線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔熟嘅<br />\n<br />\n沾麵唔係好食D咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你食過呢間既拉麵?<br />\n沾麵個麵好腍<br />\n個汁都係普通<br />\n銅鑼灣富士山55個辛辣汁好食d<br />\n不過麵質水準好唔穩定"},{"pid":"8ee28b445c1409b250c3b394d63371ac13e5550b","tid":268102,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T23:49:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食過湯麵，D麵硬過鐵線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔熟嘅<br />\n<br />\n沾麵唔係好食D咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你食過呢間既拉麵?<br />\n沾麵個麵好腍<br />\n個汁都係普通<br />\n銅鑼灣富士山55個辛辣汁好食d<br />\n不過麵質水準好唔穩定</blockquote><br />\n我食辛辣湯麵，D湯係濃，但味道好似味千果D咁<br />\n<br />\n同時見到其他枱叫湯麵嘅，都打回頭話好硬<br />\n<br />\n我坐淥麵位，睇住個哥哥仔教小朋友點煮麵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n跟本D嘢工場整好哂，只係淥麵都係搵新仔是但整比人食<br />\n<br />\n我又叫煎餃子，裡面涷嘅"},{"pid":"b27db57c61b561f258f9bde34f8562e874c8e911","tid":268102,"uid":102848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T23:52:27.000Z","msg":"沾麵都係富士55架啦"},{"pid":"5a991a3a68d98175c269e5de70a47278e5667007","tid":268102,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T23:56:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沾麵都係富士55架啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n星期一去完cwb分店<br />\n廚房d人打機、吹水、食零食、飲汽水<br />\n愈做愈hea<br />\n水準好唔穩定"},{"pid":"3f0da65bdc3a99bea55dc7adeab009dbbf571c16","tid":268102,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T00:02:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食過湯麵，D麵硬過鐵線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔熟嘅<br />\n<br />\n沾麵唔係好食D咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你食過呢間既拉麵?<br />\n沾麵個麵好腍<br />\n個汁都係普通<br />\n銅鑼灣富士山55個辛辣汁好食d<br />\n不過麵質水準好唔穩定</blockquote><br />\n我食辛辣湯麵，D湯係濃，但味道好似味千果D咁<br />\n<br />\n同時見到其他枱叫湯麵嘅，都打回頭話好硬<br />\n<br />\n我坐淥麵位，睇住個哥哥仔教小朋友點煮麵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n跟本D嘢工場整好哂，只係淥麵都係搵新仔是但整比人食<br />\n<br />\n我又叫煎餃子，裡面涷嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n試左登龍街新開嗰間未?"},{"pid":"a608effaa159098021560e29ae3958c77330ecbb","tid":268102,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T00:12:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食過湯麵，D麵硬過鐵線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔熟嘅<br />\n<br />\n沾麵唔係好食D咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你食過呢間既拉麵?<br />\n沾麵個麵好腍<br />\n個汁都係普通<br />\n銅鑼灣富士山55個辛辣汁好食d<br />\n不過麵質水準好唔穩定</blockquote><br />\n我食辛辣湯麵，D湯係濃，但味道好似味千果D咁<br />\n<br />\n同時見到其他枱叫湯麵嘅，都打回頭話好硬<br />\n<br />\n我坐淥麵位，睇住個哥哥仔教小朋友點煮麵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n跟本D嘢